<%- title 'Knowing is Half the Ballot' -%>
<div class="section">
  <h2>Knowing is Half the Ballot</h2>
  <p>At VoteReports, our politician report cards are created by people like you to condense all the complexity of politics to simple letter grades.  Simply:</p>

  <ol>
    <li><%= link_to 'Find reports', reports_path %> on the issues important to you</li>
    <li>Tell us who represents you</li>
    <li>We'll tell you how well they represent you, really</li>
  </ol>

  <% tag_cloud(@subjects, %w(css1 css2 css3 css4)) do |subject, css_class| %>
    <%= link_to subject.name, '#', :class => css_class %>
  <% end %>

  <p>Use VoteReports to see if your representatives truly represent you!</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <h2>Recent Reports</h2>
  <%= render 'reports/list', :reports => @recent_reports %>
  <%= will_paginate @recent_reports %>
</div>
